# Test Generators

## Installing

See [README](https://github.com/LibertyDSNP/test-generators/)

## Quick Start

- `npm install @dsnp/test-generators`
- Import:
  - `import * as generators from "@dsnp/test-generators";`
- Require:
  - `const generators = require("@dsnp/test-generators");`
